  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00022', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-113-ba81c82b', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-04', NULL, 'essay', '隨著氣候變遷的危機迫近，減少碳排放已是全球共識，而政策工具選擇
