品特性與一般財貨有很大的不同，因此不動產市場也不是一個完全競爭市
場。請比較與分析傳統不動產市場與完全競爭市場之異同為何。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d4005667ff0d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113130", "c": "905", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "不動產經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年專門職業及技術人員高等考試會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00024', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-113-ba81c82b', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-04', NULL, 'essay', '房價過高讓民眾無法購屋自住，很容易引起民怨，因此了解民眾對於住
