  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00027', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-113-707b521e', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-05', NULL, 'essay', '都市計畫發布實施後，原則上不得任意變更。但因應發展或特殊情事之
